 uppercase tracking-widest border border-border\">Update • News 0<!-- -->2</span></div></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-tight tracking-tight\">New Career Program for Graduates Launched</h3><p class=\"text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed line-clamp-2 font-medium\">Discover new ways to grow your career with our specialized training and global networking events.</p><div class=\"pt-4 flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 border border-border rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:border-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">Read more</span></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px) scale(0.96)\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden group rounded-[40px]\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary z-10\" style=\"transform:none\"></div><div class=\"group cursor-pointer bg-white border border-border p-8 rounded-[40px] hover:border-primary shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500\"><div class=\"aspect-video bg-zinc-100 rounded-3xl mb-10 overflow-hidden relative\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent group-hover:opacity-0 transition-opacity\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4\"><span class=\"bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest border border-border\">Update • News 0<!-- -->3</span></div></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-tight tracking-tight\">New Career Program for Graduates Launched</h3><p class=\"text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed line-clamp-2 font-medium\">Discover new ways to grow your career with our specialized training and global networking events.</p><div class=\"pt-4 flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 border border-border rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:border-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">Read more</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section-padding py-40 bg-zinc-50/50\"><div class=\"mb-24 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px) scale(0.96)\"><span class=\"text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 block\">Success Stories</span><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-4xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-black uppercase\">MEET OUR <span class=\"text-primary italic\">GRADUATES.</span></h2></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:p-12\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px) scale(0.96)\"><div class=\"bg-white p-6 md:p-12 rounded-[50px] border-2 border-zinc-100 hover:border-primary transition-all group\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 mb-8\"><div><div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-zinc-100 rounded-3xl\"></div></div><div><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Dr. Selin Yilmaz</h4><p class=\"text-primary text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">Software Architect in Berlin</p></div></div><p class=\"text-muted text-xl leading-relaxed italic\">&quot;<!-- -->The TR network helped me find my current position and connect with other Turkish engineers in Germany.<!-- -->&quot;</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px) scale(0.96)\"><div class=\"bg-white p-6 md:p-12 rounded-[50px] border-2 border-zinc-100 hover:border-primary transition-all group\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 mb-8\"><div><div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-zinc-100 rounded-3xl\"></div></div><div><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Mehmet Demir</h4><p class=\"text-primary text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">Data Scientist in London</p></div></div><p class=\"text-muted text-xl leading-relaxed italic\">&quot;<!-- -->Access to the alumni portal gave me the resources I needed to pivot my career into finance.<!-- -->&quot;</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"px-6 pb-24\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"max-w-[1400px] mx-auto bg-primary text-white rounded-[80px] p-6 md:p-20 md:p-8 md:p-32 text-center relative overflow-hidden group shadow-[0_50px_100px_-30px_rgba(225,29,72,0.4)]\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_100%_100%,rgba(255,255,255,0.2),transparent_50%)]\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[300px] h-[300px] md:w-[600px] md:h-[600px] bg-black/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2 group-hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors duration-1000\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-9xl font-bold mb-12 tracking-tighter italic leading-none\">BEYOND<br/>GRADUATION.</h2><p class=\"text-xl md:text-3xl text-white/80 mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed\">The network is live. Join our global community and take the next step in your career.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center\"><div><a class=\"bg-black text-white px-12 py-6 rounded-full font-b